      """
      Joséphine Baker: La Petite Tonkinoise / Bye Bye Blackbird
      """
    And its output should contain:
      """
      Willi Ostermann: Die Mösch / In Gold
      """
    And its output should contain:
      """
      Mick Jager: Memo From Turner / Performance
      """

